- Root cause occurrence datetime: 2021-03-09 21:00:00+08:00
- Root cause reason: Network-level connection churn / excessive TCP connection teardowns on MG02 (large TCP FIN-WAIT spike). This produced high latency (trace duration_p95 and row_count spikes) and induced cascading resource pressure (disk I/O and CPU IO-wait) on downstream services (Mysql, Redis, Tomcat, IG), causing the observed system failure.

Recommended next actions (concise):
